      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING SIGRID (2) has a strong record here including two wins from three starts. Was out of placings last time (35.07) at Sandown in a Grade 4/5, finishing fifth and beaten 3 lengths. Looks suited here and rates on top. MY NAME'S EDEN (6) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 11 lengths away in seventh (29.53). Was in the money the start prior. Goes very well from this draw with three wins and two minor placings from seven starts. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. RIVERS MEET (4) well back settling but did wind up strongly to finish 5th and beaten only 2.25 lengths (25.55) at Shepparton. Should be thereabouts. UNLEASH ME (7) dominated last start. That form reads well.",
